{"tid":480970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每一日當做生命最後一日地過活","createTime":"2017-11-26T16:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T19:17:58.000Z","uid":65743,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d13e9a6df4e80fd54834cbef86943d31a75bdad7","tid":480970,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"每一日當做生命最後一日地過活<br />\n<br />\n無人會知聽日會發生咩事<br />\n每一日都把握好時間<br />\n每一日都盡力做到最好<br />\n每一日都要過得充實/有意義/開心<br />\n唔好枉過每一日<br />\n當發現今日就係最後一日<br />\n就好比自己後悔<br />\n<br />\n積極過每一日<br />\n人生只有兩三萬日.."},{"pid":"b8b93ba1eda43a780b794ad04d207ff2858fa6c1","tid":480970,"uid":5806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:31:18.000Z","msg":"安安靜靜咁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢睇下身邊嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed1dc996f07d3de23dde9ca1ef0941acccca71f","tid":480970,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"生命最後果一日都唔輕輕鬆鬆過<br />\n死左去吧啦"},{"pid":"afb7c613b691649b5472036926b315f795155645","tid":480970,"uid":30604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"就每天當沒明天 捉緊愛人過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310074c8e53b94d86eda5af8a04928141e24db7f","tid":480970,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"我想吃掉你的胰臟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52c40d4dc2abd6faca559011c0646524479ce38","tid":480970,"uid":81256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:37:37.000Z","msg":"呢個idea唔知俾幾多人抄上抄"},{"pid":"bd656c49578a3c83fa068e18f01bca9111a69669","tid":480970,"uid":22876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/004052_dc503f474170d0e4c8577307b92322ff.jpg\" data-thumb